//Welcome
// How to cook chicken biryani
// Soak large size riped biryani for 15-30 mins
// mix 2tbspoon oil, or ghee into it and boil for 12 - 15 mins
// marinate chicken for 3 hours
// start cooking the chicken for 30 mins after mixing enough water
//drain excess water from the biryani and mix into the chicken bowl
// put a lid, and close its surroundings with silver foil and cook on sim for 20 mins
// call navin to taste it and then stop the stove
